The TV personality recently celebrated his 30th birthday in a surprise sunset cruise aboard the luxury catamaran Mirage 760 with just under 100 of his closest friends, family and colleagues.The three hour cruise set sail from the V&amp;A Waterfront in the late afternoon and anchored in Granger Bay for a speech by fellow Expresso presenter Graeme Richards, cake, champagne and celebrations by the light of a golden Capetonian sunset.Among those in attendance were Katlego s mother, younger sister and of course, his bae, who he rightfully showed off.While we're not sure what her name is, all you need to know is that she's a Liesl Laurie look-alike, and she's smoking-hot.(All pictures have been provided by Michael Le Grange) Find the hottest celebrity and entertainment news on TshisaLIVE or follow TshisaLIVE on Facebook and Twitter.